channel.title: Natural Born Killers: Release
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i46.tinypic.com/no6l2g.png[/img][/center]
Hey everyone. Sorry about earlier but this is the official release of my server project. This is my server project which unfortunately turned dead. I tried as hard as I could to bring in players but unfortunately I failed. Jmood123 was hosting for me which provided a fantastic opportunity but 1-5 players online average was not enough. So I am releasing it. It is an edited version of the ever so popular Project Insanity. I'm not going to say this is absolutely revolutionary programming but I would recommend you download this version as it has new interfaces and almost all bugs & dupes removed.
[b]Important[/b]: If you don't like players using noclip; search for it in Client.java > Client sided and remove it. This loads all [b]474[/b] items through the cache. If you want to spawn items use a 474 item list. If the client doesn't open when you click Run, replace it with this: [code]@echo off title Natural Born Killers java -Xmx300m Jframe 10 0 highmem members 32 pause[/code] Re-enabling player follow. Search for: [code=java] getPA().showOption(4, 0,"Trade With", 3);[/code] Underneath it place: [code=java] getPA().showOption(5, 0,"Follow", 4);[/code] Package Size: 22.51mb Download: http://www.mediafire.com/?yyjhzmo3qmm
Here is several but not all updates which I have recorded.
• Changed layout of the server and moved home/pking spots to more conveniant places • Fixed the offer x amount dupe • Crash patched the server via IsaacRandomGen class - Thanks blakeman8912 • Fixed the dueling dupe where if you logout during a duel the opposing player is forced to flee giving you the staked items. • Extended player save • Ranked yelling system • Fixed the original godwars now has three bosses + minions and will be adding the fourth shortly • Fixed attack with magic out of wilderness, players now can only attack each other with magic in pvp zones • Added ancient curses interface • 100% Pest control interfaces • Added world map .jar • Stabilized • Loaded SWAT's new animations header
Etc. Can't be bothered with the rest of the updates, you can find out yourself. Now for some pictures. These are the pictures I used for advertisement so don't complain if they don't show the full extent.

I do plan to improve on this in the next month or so and may release a Natural Born Killers v2.0. I however will not be hosting a server again. Big thanks to Jmood123 for hosting and Amayzing for an IPB 3.0 board.
If anyone has any questions regarding the client/server feel free to private message me as I have become extemely familiar with the layout.
If you want to upload a mirror of the package then please feel free to do so and post here as it took me almost two hours to upload one because of my scrappy upload speed.
Enjoy.
